{"tid":1399593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[心機野] 旺角圍欄地圖：香港仲有咩路行？","createTime":"2019-08-03T08:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T08:16:30.000Z","uid":265313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0c6b253da9772b995dea0eec4d2de09d092bd8","tid":1399593,"uid":265313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:16:30.000Z","msg":"facebook見到，鍾意行街嘅巴打應該好有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxTM5Te.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhxTM5Te.jpg&h=1103486c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n//單係旺角，已經 #周圍都係欄。比較常見嘅直間同橫間鐵欄（圖中黃色），設計簡單啲，少啲螺絲位。另外有一種特式鐵欄（圖中橙色），呢種欄設計特別穩固。<br />\n<br />\n要做到「還街於民」，城市規劃上需要以行人為本，首要當然係認出一啲無無謂謂嘅圍欄，所以我哋製作呢個「圍欄地圖」，畀市民、行人得閒去旺角食好西、鳩嗚嘅時候，諗吓路邊嘅圍欄係咪必要、邊啲圍欄係多餘，令香港變得更「好行」。//<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongMyFuture/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongMyFuture%2F&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsSVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=717a34c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongMyFuture/</a>"}]}